A family branded the 'original neighbours from hell' was finally evicted from their council house today after 97 separate incidents of anti-social behaviour.

The four members of the Newell family abused, spat at and threatened to kill residents in Mountain Ash, South Wales, who put up with three years of 'total misery'.

A court heard the Newells made so much noise shouting and screaming that their next door neighbours had to watch television with subtitles.

